<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
<Header pageTitle={"questioning akuyu (qa)"} description={""} />
<style>
    main {
        width: 960px;
    }
    p, ul {
        margin-bottom: 34px;
    }

    a {
        color: black;
        text-decoration: none;
    }

    a:hover {
        color: var(--accent);
    }
</style>

<body>
<main>
    <h2>questions which you <i>might</i> want hear answers to</h2>
    <p>Q: why the hell does your website has this domain and pages look like this??<br>
        A: domain part: idk i just was just browsing something online and saw .rip domain and then i thought about
        ame (nso) for some reason and it clicked and i was like  "oh wow this sounds great i really should do this" and so i did.
				 initially i though of taking akuyu.dev but then this idea popped up, so yeah, not exactly inspiring<br>
        design part: because i am not particularly good at coming up with
        graphics-related things so i just got inspired by nso's window layout and decided to commit to the bit. at first
        i had much more interesting idea but then i scrapped it because i dont know how to work with graphics in browsers
        so i decided to delay it and went with <i>this</i>
    </p>
    <p>
        Q: you piss me off and you should grow up and change as a person!!<br>
        A: sorry... but also nope i am not really willing to change or grow up for that matter, i do sound more normal
        irl when i talk to people and they seem to like me so idk, draw conclusions yourself
