    <p>
        Q: wow i think ur cool what do you even do in your life?<br>
        A: yeah no i am not cool by any means and my life is not even interesting, just a regular life.
        its not that boring though, sometimes i get incredible human to human interactions which leave me perplexed
        (maybe i should get a separate page to share them, idk)
    </p>
    <p>
        Q: what do you like?<br>
        A: sleeping. but i dont get enough of sleep.... i also really really like talking about my interests
    </p>
    <p>
        Q: what do you not like then?<br>
        A: fake people. like really dont like them. i also dont like overly serious people. like imagine
        always being serious - that is no fun, especially when you try to approach people like that, theres literally no angle to do that from<br>
        i also dont like heat and hot weather, absolutely disgusting, winter and lukewarm places for the win
        (although summer evening are incredible and probably only good thing about warm/hot seasons)
    </p>
    <p>
        Q: you mentioned interests, what are you interested in?<br>
        A: i used to play a lot of games (mostly indie), so naturally i like games. it would be logical to list games
        i like here but eeh, dont wanna (although you can probably see one that i really like already :^))<br>
        i also really really like music i listen to and im not limited to one genre (although theres definitely a dominating one)
    </p>
    <p>
        Q: do you "fw" [some specific thing]?<br>
        A: quick and inaccurate answer: if this thing is extremely popular then theres a good chance that no,
        otherwise almost always yes.
        in any case you can just ask me directly if you want to know for sure
    </p>
    <p>
        Q: where are you from? how old are you? ...and other not so interesting questions<br>
        A: knowing answers would change nothing so not telling... ill let this be a small guessing game for now though,
        tbh it shouldnt be that hard to guess (hint: i am far from being old and im located somewhere in eu)
    </p>
    <p>
        this concludes qa page for now, might add/remove entries in the future.
    </p>
</main>
</body>
</html>
